FiltreLogin - Class in fr.gtm.formation.proxibanque.filtre
This class is a Servlet Filter witch implement class FiltreLogin
This class allows the access to all the application pages if the user in session ('avdisor') is logged in
If the user is not logged in, the filter redirect to the login page
